No current device is as universal as the phone.
In addition to primary functions, telephone calls and SMS sending, it is able to read music and films, record them, it has a variable quality camera and can, for example, be used for navigation.
And if we take Smartphones and communicators into account, you'll have a little computer in your pocket.
Since no fridge can grill meat and no television will take photographs, we are almost seeing a miracle.
