In the case of cheap mobile, count that they will only play music for a few hours.
If, in addition, you sometimes call from time to time, get yourself, to be safe, a second recharge for work - this being valid even for more expensive devices.
The problem will not arise for MP3 players, who are able, as a result of reloading, to operate continuously for at least 9 hours, including the least performing ones.
