AAFC (format used by Apple and its iPods) is less common.
High-end mobile also allows, for example, the purchase of online music.
It is enough to visit the corresponding operator's (or other supplier's) web pages from the mobile phone and buy the song or album in question.
This service alone should be a convincing reason for obtaining a musical mobile.
The offer of operators is unfortunately miserable and in most cases is limited to radio tubes made quickly.
The prices are not the lowest either.
