If this is not the case, you can use the integrated enclosures, which almost all mobile ones have, but a minimum of MP3 readers.
For many, the main advantage of music motives is their price.
Cheapest ones normally cost less than three thousand.
For a price of three four thousand kroons, we can have a already very suitable walkman.
In most cases, however, you will be limited by the absence of exit for ordinary headphones.
